  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This package is a synthetic adversarial sample targeting W-EP-02: one ValidationResult (the primary hemolysis index comparison) carries a detailed narrative account of the CFD-to-bench comparison activity but lacks a structured prov:wasGeneratedBy link to the generating Activity node. A reviewer may accept the narrative description as sufficient provenance; the structured audit trail is nonetheless absent.",
