      "description": "Steady-state CFD pressure-head predictions were compared against published experimental HQ curves from the FDA interlaboratory study (Hariharan et al. 2011). Agreement within 5% was achieved across the operating envelope, confirming adequate hydraulic fidelity of the mesh and boundary conditions prior to hemolysis integration."
    },
